data.title: who am i
data.subTitle: Hello! I am Islam Nasser. Mobile Application Development Team lead.
data.description:
As a highly skilled Mobile Team Lead with 7+ years of experience in iOS and Android app
development, I specialize in leading cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality mobile
solutions using Flutter. My experience spans across developing robust applications for both
platforms, mentoring developers, and driving the successful launch of over 20 apps on the
Google Play and Apple App Store,

I excel in agile project management, team coordination, and creating scalable solutions that
align with business goals. Passionate about innovation and problem-solving and professional
growth, I am looking to leverage my leadership skills to drive impactful results and contribute
to the success of a forward-thinking organization.
